job.title: Senior Software Engineer - Biotech
job.description: If you are a Senior Software Engineer with experience, please read on! We are treating mental health disorders with our ground-breaking novel therapeutics. Top Reasons to Work with Us Great Location Great Hiring Manager Take your career to the next level What You Will Be Doing As the Senior Software Engineer, you will be responsible for developing different projects, mostly on the back end. There will be some front end work. You will develpo back-end APIs and integrate our 3rd party APIs into our front-end apps. You will also devise features and maintain them. What You Need for this Position BS in Comp Sci or Equivalent SQL RESTful APIs React/React native CSS SQL ES6/Typescript What's In It for You Competitive Salary Results-driven environment Benefits So, if you are a Senior Software Engineer with experience, please apply today! Email Your Resume In Word To Looking forward to receiving your resume through our website and going over the position with you. Clicking apply is the best way to apply, but you may also: Alexander.Charles@CyberCoders.com Please do NOT change the email subject line in any way. You must keep the JobID: linkedin : AC11-1645049 -- in the email subject line for your application to be considered.*** Alexander Charles - Recruiter - CyberCoders Applicants must be authorized to work in the U.S. CyberCoders, Inc is proud to be an Equal Opportunity Employer All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, sex, national origin, disability, protected veteran status, or any other characteristic protected by law.
